<plot>Bernard Bradbury is a Repo Man who works for GlobalNet BioMedical, a company that leases organs and limbs. Bernie spends his days repossessing fetuses and penile prosthetics. Unknown to Bernard, he's been declared obsolete: there's a new and improved model on the market and Bernard is targeted for repossession himself.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?158200</url></doc>
